83
00:06:37,130 --> 00:06:38,440
It'll save me some effort.

84
00:06:38,460 --> 00:06:39,930
How dare you slack off?

85
00:06:40,070 --> 00:06:41,630
Then we'll just build a cat house.

86
00:06:41,659 --> 00:06:42,980
And you live there with Jiaoniang, alright?

87
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:43,840
We...

88
00:06:43,870 --> 00:06:44,940
Alright.

89
00:06:44,970 --> 00:06:46,680
Stop arguing. It's not a big deal.

90
00:06:46,830 --> 00:06:48,110
Let's all work hard together.

91
00:06:48,140 --> 00:06:49,990
More hands make light work, okay?

92
00:06:50,070 --> 00:06:53,140
You're right. I'll be careful.

93
00:06:53,310 --> 00:06:53,810
Alright.

94
