116
00:08:09,200 --> 00:08:10,470
Are you here to help too?

117
00:08:10,500 --> 00:08:11,060
Come on.

118
00:08:16,030 --> 00:08:17,610
I told you not to go, didn't I?

119
00:08:18,270 --> 00:08:19,790
You're just asking for trouble.

120
00:08:21,710 --> 00:08:23,000
What are you doing here?

121
00:08:23,950 --> 00:08:25,580
There's so much work to do, and you're not helping.

122
00:08:25,880 --> 00:08:26,920
Come help me move this stuff!

123
00:08:28,590 --> 00:08:30,500
Let's go, down there.

124
00:08:33,100 --> 00:08:33,940
Down there.

125
00:08:41,150 --> 00:08:41,919
Tighten it.

126
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:43,720
Down you go.

127
00:08:45,910 --> 00:08:46,990
I'll kick you if you don't move!

128
00:08:49,400 --> 00:08:50,170
Get in there!

129
00:08:50,560 --> 00:08:51,330
Help out!

130
00:08:51,790 --> 00:08:54,200
They're really a perfect pair, huh?

131
00:08:54,270 --> 00:08:55,280
Get inside!

132
00:08:57,720 --> 00:09:00,140
Weren't you here to help? Then help!

133
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:03,750
