136
00:09:07,480 --> 00:09:09,520
You've got some nerve!

137
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:10,800
Hurry up and get to work!

138
00:09:11,430 --> 00:09:13,370
Go help.

139
00:09:18,560 --> 00:09:19,530
Hurry up.

140
00:09:25,410 --> 00:09:26,460
Are you okay?

141
00:09:26,490 --> 00:09:27,380
It's okay.

142
00:09:35,800 --> 00:09:36,560
Throw it up.

143
00:09:39,110 --> 00:09:40,810
I told you not to get involved.

144
00:09:41,220 --> 00:09:43,410
You're not cut out for this kind of work.

145
00:09:50,220 --> 00:09:51,310
You alright?

146
00:09:51,330 --> 00:09:52,040
Yeah, I'm fine.

147
00:09:52,990 --> 00:09:53,910
Let me see.

148
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:55,470
I'm fine.

149
00:09:56,330 --> 00:09:57,360
Just put some medicine on it.

150
00:10:00,360 --> 00:10:01,440
We're

151
00:10:01,460 --> 00:10:03,440
