153
00:10:11,870 --> 00:10:12,840
Thank you.

154
00:10:14,840 --> 00:10:17,290
You'd better not meddle in this kind of rough work.

155
00:10:17,370 --> 00:10:18,370
Let's keep going.

156
00:10:18,620 --> 00:10:19,840
