157
00:10:32,330 --> 00:10:33,330
Alright, come on.

158
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:35,850
Not bad!

159
00:10:35,880 --> 00:10:37,610
You're actually pulling your weight.

160
00:10:38,710 --> 00:10:42,180
People live to learn endlessly.

161
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:43,560
To stop learning is to stagnate.

162
00:10:44,380 --> 00:10:46,570
The scariest thing is laziness,

163
00:10:47,570 --> 00:10:49,060
