368
00:19:53,450 --> 00:19:54,910
Hurry up and sweep!

369
00:19:54,940 --> 00:19:56,180
Hurry up and sweep!

370
00:19:57,490 --> 00:19:58,220
Sweep!

371
00:19:58,240 --> 00:19:59,200
Hurry!

