390
00:21:01,660 --> 00:21:03,400
They're all commoners.

391
00:21:03,490 --> 00:21:05,070
We can't resort to extreme measures.

392
00:21:07,520 --> 00:21:09,370
We could try building a good relationship with them.

393
00:21:09,400 --> 00:21:10,630
We can appeal to emotions.

394
00:21:11,490 --> 00:21:12,460
Can you do that?

395
00:21:13,630 --> 00:21:14,940
When it comes to forming connections,

396
00:21:14,970 --> 00:21:17,030
