397
00:21:17,500 --> 00:21:18,360
Alright.

398
00:21:18,730 --> 00:21:19,540
You go ahead then.

399
00:21:19,560 --> 00:21:20,760
Bring along that Han Aizhen.

400
00:21:21,090 --> 00:21:22,990
