426
00:22:45,940 --> 00:22:46,800
Super cool?

427
00:22:47,730 --> 00:22:48,730
How cool can it be?

428
00:22:52,490 --> 00:22:53,410
Let me try.

429
00:24:05,090 --> 00:24:06,680
