431
00:24:16,140 --> 00:24:19,080
Weird. So weird.

432
00:24:27,720 --> 00:24:28,590
A ghost!

433
00:24:28,690 --> 00:24:30,720
Hong Hui, what are you doing?

434
00:24:31,430 --> 00:24:33,560
No, this is cool!

435
00:24:35,830 --> 00:24:36,830
Not bad.

436
00:24:53,730 --> 00:24:55,190
Is this

437
00:24:56,380 --> 00:25:00,630
