438
00:25:01,240 --> 00:25:03,150
Cool. Super cool.

439
00:25:04,480 --> 00:25:05,470
Looks good.

440
00:25:05,930 --> 00:25:06,910
Cool works.

441
00:25:07,930 --> 00:25:09,590
Ghosts are the coolest. They scare everyone.

442
00:25:09,990 --> 00:25:11,110
Alright, let's keep it.

443
00:25:11,130 --> 00:25:11,910
I'm quite satisfied.

444
00:25:14,800 --> 00:25:15,670
Of course,

445
00:25:15,950 --> 00:25:17,380
for makeup like this,

446
00:25:17,400 --> 00:25:19,320
