447
00:25:19,410 --> 00:25:20,710
Come on, let's change clothes.

448
00:25:21,030 --> 00:25:21,720
Let's change.

449
00:25:24,020 --> 00:25:25,190
I look cool.

450
00:25:25,190 --> 00:25:25,990
You do look cool.

451
00:25:41,910 --> 00:25:43,390
So weird.

452
00:25:43,910 --> 00:25:46,270
