471
00:26:41,080 --> 00:26:44,110
earth-shattering and ghost-weeping cool!

472
00:26:44,380 --> 00:26:46,750
Hong Hui, no favoritism!

473
00:26:48,130 --> 00:26:49,150
Alright, let's do it.

474
00:26:52,070 --> 00:26:53,350
Hong Hui.

475
00:27:00,460 --> 00:27:01,870
Wow, it looks great!

476
00:27:15,880 --> 00:27:16,710
Cool.

477
00:27:18,610 --> 00:27:20,030
Really pretty.

478
00:27:20,420 --> 00:27:21,350
Yes.

479
00:27:30,120 --> 00:27:30,790
Well.

480
00:27:31,840 --> 00:27:32,630
This...

481
00:27:33,560 --> 00:27:35,320
