482
00:27:35,340 --> 00:27:36,510
This...

483
00:27:36,920 --> 00:27:39,630
Isn't this like that, uh, banshee or something?

484
00:27:40,350 --> 00:27:41,950
This is what cool looks like!

485
00:27:41,970 --> 00:27:43,230
How is this not cool?

486
00:27:43,710 --> 00:27:44,970
In my heart,

487
00:27:45,650 --> 00:27:47,660
you're the most perfect goddess!

488
00:27:51,720 --> 00:27:53,670
