542
00:30:33,350 --> 00:30:34,270
You...

543
00:30:36,440 --> 00:30:37,350
Look at you.

544
00:30:37,620 --> 00:30:39,210
You have a delicate heart,

545
00:30:39,370 --> 00:30:40,670
pure nature,

546
00:30:40,690 --> 00:30:42,390
