547
00:30:44,450 --> 00:30:47,560
You're simply a charming person loved by everyone.

548
00:30:47,940 --> 00:30:49,390
You really know how to talk.

549
00:30:51,140 --> 00:30:52,390
I'll let bygones

550
00:30:52,410 --> 00:30:53,540
