551
00:30:53,980 --> 00:30:55,610
I knew I didn't misjudge you.

552
00:30:55,670 --> 00:30:57,230
You're the most tolerant and magnanimous person.

553
00:30:57,330 --> 00:30:59,130
It's just a pity that I'm not a man.

554
00:31:00,160 --> 00:31:01,710
Unlike some people,

555
00:31:01,720 --> 00:31:03,760
