556
00:31:11,860 --> 00:31:14,610
Hong Hui, did you forget something?

557
00:31:14,720 --> 00:31:16,160
It's time to do our makeup.

558
00:31:23,970 --> 00:31:24,650
Hey!

559
00:31:25,480 --> 00:31:26,850
What's wrong?

560
00:31:28,270 --> 00:31:29,460
Snap out of it.

561
00:31:30,680 --> 00:31:31,950
We need to do our makeup.

562
00:31:36,090 --> 00:31:36,930
Straightforward

563
00:31:37,890 --> 00:31:38,650
and simple.

564
00:31:39,990 --> 00:31:41,830
