565
00:31:43,080 --> 00:31:44,450
Tomboy?

566
00:31:44,890 --> 00:31:46,040
Fine, tomboy it is.

567
00:31:46,070 --> 00:31:48,070
Give me a warrior woman look.

568
00:31:48,640 --> 00:31:49,400
Got it!

569
00:31:49,410 --> 00:31:50,020
Here you go.

570
00:32:10,670 --> 00:32:12,290
This is a warrior woman look?

571
00:32:12,430 --> 00:32:13,770
Just putting on a straw hat?

572
00:32:14,700 --> 00:32:17,620
If there were a real fight, wouldn't it be a burden?

573
00:32:19,870 --> 00:32:21,470
Makeup is an art.

574
00:32:21,520 --> 00:32:23,410
Art always has to be a bit complicated.

575
00:32:24,250 --> 00:32:27,060
I just feel awkward.

576
00:32:27,250 --> 00:32:28,370
Do I look awkward to you?

577
00:32:30,580 --> 00:32:31,380
Awkward.

578
00:32:31,840 --> 00:32:32,860
See? There you go.

579
00:32:33,840 --> 00:32:36,400
The problem is, whether you wear makeup or not, I still feel awkward.

580
00:32:37,470 --> 00:32:38,480
That's normal,

581
00:32:38,590 --> 00:32:40,110
because we're not the same kind.

582
00:32:41,100 --> 00:32:42,800
You and Wang Yishao are the same kind?

583
00:32:43,150 --> 00:32:44,860
You hang out together every day.

584
00:32:44,900 --> 00:32:46,840
That's because you don't understand him.

585
00:32:47,430 --> 00:32:50,710
The person you see isn't the real him.

586
00:32:52,990 --> 00:32:55,310
What's the real him like?

587
00:32:57,120 --> 00:32:58,030
Look over there.

588
00:32:58,600 --> 00:33:00,480
Just like that person.

589
00:33:04,230 --> 00:33:06,660
Wang Yishao is also a beggar?

590
00:33:06,840 --> 00:33:08,150
What beggar?

591
00:33:08,710 --> 00:33:11,870
He's an immortal. Get it?

592
00:33:12,470 --> 00:33:15,390
Wang Yishao barely qualifies as an immortal.

593
00:33:16,380 --> 00:33:18,020
But you? You don't even come close.

594
00:33:18,990 --> 00:33:21,680
Me? I'm a demon.

595
00:33:24,240 --> 00:33:25,660
You're a demon, a monster, a ghost.

596
00:33:26,020 --> 00:33:29,130
Wang Yishao and his kind are immortals who subdue demons and exorcise spirits.

597
00:33:29,220 --> 00:33:31,180
You're their pet, right?

598
00:33:34,160 --> 00:33:36,210
You've spent so much time talking to me.

599
00:33:36,230 --> 00:33:38,180
You've forgotten what you're supposed to be doing.

600
00:33:42,240 --> 00:33:45,320
Now, look at them. Are they immortals or demons?

601
00:33:46,200 --> 00:33:49,000
You two are starting to sound more and more like Qing Cai.

602
00:33:50,970 --> 00:33:53,220
Alright, give the two of us a makeover too.

603
00:33:53,560 --> 00:33:55,080
Let's see what we turn into.

604
00:33:57,050 --> 00:33:57,750
Alright, alright.

605
00:33:57,780 --> 00:33:58,260
Sure.

606
00:34:06,780 --> 00:34:08,340
This is too much!

607
00:34:08,469 --> 00:34:10,960
Real immortals and demons wouldn't be any more over the top than this.

608
00:34:11,400 --> 00:34:12,449
Demons are great!

609
00:34:12,520 --> 00:34:14,760
Doesn't that make me, a ghost, a perfect match for you?

610
00:34:26,850 --> 00:34:28,449
Enduring countless storms,

611
00:34:28,840 --> 00:34:30,020
growing strong,

612
00:34:30,370 --> 00:34:31,480
like wild grass.

613
00:34:32,400 --> 00:34:35,370
Not fragrant, but beautiful in its own way.

614
00:34:36,460 --> 00:34:37,350
Are you talking about me?

615
00:34:50,500 --> 00:34:51,409
What's up?

616
00:34:53,010 --> 00:34:55,270
You two, one is a flower, and the other is grass.

617
00:34:55,469 --> 00:34:56,800
You really are kindred spirits.

618
00:34:59,460 --> 00:35:01,160
We're just humble weeds.

619
00:35:02,060 --> 00:35:04,120
If you're calling yourselves weeds,

620
00:35:04,170 --> 00:35:07,230
then unrivaled beauty would be reduced to beggars.

621
00:35:08,590 --> 00:35:10,670
You've gotten good at sarcasm now.

622
00:35:18,080 --> 00:35:19,340
Looking at you,

623
00:35:19,570 --> 00:35:22,000
I now understand why you use poison.

624
00:35:24,500 --> 00:35:25,800
See this?

625
00:35:26,160 --> 00:35:27,660
It's my dual nature.

626
00:35:29,140 --> 00:35:30,020
Gan Pu,

627
00:35:32,010 --> 00:35:34,490
your makeup is absolutely stunning.

628
00:35:34,770 --> 00:35:35,520
Is it?

629
00:35:36,640 --> 00:35:37,560
Young Master Wang,

630
00:35:37,690 --> 00:35:39,850
aren't you only supposed to care about inner beauty?

631
00:35:39,880 --> 00:35:41,900
How could you be bewitched by such an illusion?

632
00:35:42,370 --> 00:35:45,880
When someone is beautiful without realizing or caring about it,

633
00:35:46,270 --> 00:35:47,510
that is true beauty.

634
00:35:48,790 --> 00:35:50,590
Are you complimenting me? Thank you.

635
00:35:52,650 --> 00:35:55,420
Young Master Wang, your flattery skills

636
00:35:55,450 --> 00:35:56,690
are simply outrageous.

637
00:35:56,930 --> 00:35:58,080
You're quite impressive too,

638
00:35:59,070 --> 00:36:00,950
managing to insult two people with one sentence.

639
00:36:04,290 --> 00:36:05,750
Gan Pu is my sister.

640
00:36:06,490 --> 00:36:07,550
How could I insult her?

641
00:36:07,760 --> 00:36:09,470
Actually, praising her is the same as praising me.

642
00:36:13,570 --> 00:36:16,610
Your sister doesn't seem to think much of you, though.

643
00:36:20,430 --> 00:36:21,190
Gao Yin,

644
00:36:21,610 --> 00:36:24,630
don't take anything Qing Cai does to heart.

645
00:36:25,150 --> 00:36:26,080
Thank you.

646
00:36:28,190 --> 00:36:30,870
You really are considerate of her.

647
00:36:32,420 --> 00:36:34,870
Aren't you being too noble?

648
00:36:35,300 --> 00:36:35,940
You…

649
00:36:38,540 --> 00:36:40,160
You even noticed that.

650
00:36:42,500 --> 00:36:44,750
If I didn't know his identity,

651
00:36:45,400 --> 00:36:46,620
I'd find it strange too.

652
00:36:48,880 --> 00:36:50,200
Just like Young Master Wang.

653
00:36:55,730 --> 00:36:57,240
What a waste!

654
00:36:57,680 --> 00:36:58,590
This is just too beautiful.

655
00:36:58,590 --> 00:36:59,990
This is the last jar.

656
00:37:01,120 --> 00:37:03,790
No way. I need to buy more wine.

657
00:37:05,600 --> 00:37:07,060
What a strange person.

658
00:37:13,220 --> 00:37:14,080
Not bad.

659
00:37:18,280 --> 00:37:19,410
It's very slimming.

660
00:37:20,240 --> 00:37:21,430
Although it's a bit over the top,

661
00:37:21,450 --> 00:37:22,700
it's quite unique.

662
00:37:24,040 --> 00:37:25,860
How about we head back to the town

663
00:37:25,900 --> 00:37:27,720
to test the look?

664
00:37:27,740 --> 00:37:29,870
Sure, let's all go to the town together.

665
00:37:30,370 --> 00:37:31,890
If we're going to town,

666
00:37:31,910 --> 00:37:32,760
I need to remove this makeup.

667
00:37:32,790 --> 00:37:33,160
No way.

668
00:37:33,180 --> 00:37:34,050
-No.
-No.

669
00:37:34,090 --> 00:37:34,580
No way.

670
00:37:45,390 --> 00:37:46,140
Then…

671
00:37:48,030 --> 00:37:51,010
Since we're all wearing makeup now,

672
00:37:51,040 --> 00:37:52,350
Young Master Wang is the only one left without it.

673
00:37:52,380 --> 00:37:54,100
Young Master Wang should get some makeup done too.

674
00:37:54,910 --> 00:37:55,950
Yes, yes.

675
00:37:55,980 --> 00:37:57,460
You're one of us.

676
00:37:57,480 --> 00:37:58,550
We can't leave you out.

677
00:38:02,050 --> 00:38:02,970
Young Master Wang,

678
00:38:02,990 --> 00:38:05,270
we've just learned how to do makeup.

679
00:38:05,300 --> 00:38:06,470
Shouldn't we at least

680
00:38:06,490 --> 00:38:08,080
get some practice?

681
00:38:08,120 --> 00:38:09,660
Here, let me do your makeup.

682
00:38:13,500 --> 00:38:15,210
I know you're targeting me.

683
00:38:15,680 --> 00:38:16,440
It's fine.

684
00:38:17,400 --> 00:38:18,070
I'll do it.

685
00:38:34,520 --> 00:38:36,050
What kind of invisibility technique did you teach?

686
00:38:36,070 --> 00:38:37,950
Everyone surrounding us can see this!

687
00:38:38,640 --> 00:38:40,140
This is so much fun!

688
00:38:40,160 --> 00:38:41,520
I've never played like this before.

689
00:38:41,550 --> 00:38:42,710
It's really fun.

690
00:38:43,490 --> 00:38:46,500
Is your life really that boring?

691
00:38:46,650 --> 00:38:47,970
You call this fun?

692
00:38:48,360 --> 00:38:49,260
Yes.

693
00:38:49,300 --> 00:38:51,100
I have endless things to deal with every day,

694
00:38:51,120 --> 00:38:52,810
and it's truly dull.

695
00:38:54,330 --> 00:38:57,240
Actually, life in the Wang residence is boring

696
00:38:57,280 --> 00:38:58,160
and stifling too.

697
00:38:58,830 --> 00:39:00,190
It's uninteresting.

698
00:39:04,300 --> 00:39:06,010
Hong Hui, are you treating me like a monkey for your amusement?

699
00:39:06,030 --> 00:39:07,710
Wait until I get back, I'll break your neck!

700
00:39:07,740 --> 00:39:09,420
Hong Hui, she's going to break your neck.

701
00:39:09,440 --> 00:39:11,240
Is it really that stifling?

702
00:39:12,540 --> 00:39:14,420
They've all gone mad.

703
00:39:14,970 --> 00:39:15,970
Alright,

704
00:39:16,200 --> 00:39:17,750
it seems like I'm the only sane person

705
00:39:17,790 --> 00:39:19,630
left in this world.

706
00:39:21,600 --> 00:39:22,690
Yishao,

707
00:39:24,380 --> 00:39:27,950
Your subordinate is really worrisome.

708
00:39:30,930 --> 00:39:32,730
You know he's working for me.

709
00:39:34,470 --> 00:39:35,470
I know.

710
00:39:36,320 --> 00:39:37,880
Women should act a bit naive,

711
00:39:38,260 --> 00:39:39,590
or at least

712
00:39:41,160 --> 00:39:42,730
pretend to be naive.

713
00:39:44,550 --> 00:39:45,950
But I don't like pretending.

714
00:39:47,360 --> 00:39:48,850
That's not the reason.

715
00:39:50,590 --> 00:39:51,900
Actually, I know.

716
00:39:52,570 --> 00:39:54,280
I was just overthinking.

717
00:39:57,190 --> 00:39:58,940
Everyone has a vulnerable side.

718
00:40:01,040 --> 00:40:02,910
If I were to become Emperor,

719
00:40:03,900 --> 00:40:05,470
you'd be my first choice.

720
00:40:10,660 --> 00:40:11,670
Yes,

721
00:40:13,170 --> 00:40:15,070
an emperor cannot act on emotions.

722
00:40:18,760 --> 00:40:19,800
I'm sorry.

723
00:40:20,490 --> 00:40:22,080
I didn't mean to offend you.

724
00:40:22,100 --> 00:40:23,210
I understand.

725
00:40:24,920 --> 00:40:26,110
Emotions are born

726
00:40:27,170 --> 00:40:28,810
from the heart.

727
00:40:28,980 --> 00:40:30,900
You don't know when they begin,

728
00:40:33,310 --> 00:40:35,170
nor can you control them.

729
00:40:51,460 --> 00:40:52,660
You and Aizhen…

730
00:40:56,200 --> 00:40:57,250
She's my sister.

731
00:41:04,590 --> 00:41:06,100
I used to think

732
00:41:06,930 --> 00:41:08,710
you were an ordinary person like me.

733
00:41:09,010 --> 00:41:10,890
But now, with your identity,

734
00:41:11,370 --> 00:41:13,030
you feel so distant

735
00:41:14,200 --> 00:41:15,320
and so unfamiliar.

736
00:41:20,040 --> 00:41:21,320
Do you think I've changed?

737
00:41:23,220 --> 00:41:24,620
It's hard to say about the future.

738
00:41:26,280 --> 00:41:29,780
Do you think it's necessary for us to even think about the future?

739
00:41:38,800 --> 00:41:39,990
You're right.

740
00:41:42,780 --> 00:41:44,820
Someone like me, who has no future,

741
00:41:46,050 --> 00:41:47,340
what's the point of talking about it?

742
00:41:47,800 --> 00:41:51,170
Just surviving this long is already a blessing.

743
00:41:52,820 --> 00:41:54,180
What I mean is,

744
00:41:54,640 --> 00:41:56,720
I feel the same as you.

745
00:41:57,330 --> 00:41:59,530
The future seems so uncertain.

746
00:42:00,720 --> 00:42:03,790
What we can do now is live in the present.

747
00:42:05,480 --> 00:42:06,450
And,

748
00:42:07,440 --> 00:42:08,610
even in death,

749
00:42:10,800 --> 00:42:12,670
we wouldn't walk the Yellow Springs road alone.

750
00:42:29,050 --> 00:42:31,270
Do you know why I'm willing to accept you?

751
00:42:32,890 --> 00:42:33,790
I know.

752
00:42:38,860 --> 00:42:39,720
Qing Cai,

753
00:42:41,090 --> 00:42:42,130
thank you.

754
00:42:44,720 --> 00:42:45,850
Really, thank you.

755
00:42:57,880 --> 00:42:59,160
There are so many people here today.

756
00:42:59,630 --> 00:43:00,860
Thank you.

757
00:43:00,880 --> 00:43:02,450
Thank you, everyone.

758
00:43:02,470 --> 00:43:03,460
Thank you.

759
00:43:03,940 --> 00:43:06,470
Today, I'll share with you the most relaxing,

760
00:43:06,580 --> 00:43:09,390
most enjoyable story I know.

761
00:43:11,130 --> 00:43:11,930
Speaking of which...

762
00:43:11,950 --> 00:43:12,950
I don't want to play anymore.

763
00:43:13,550 --> 00:43:14,720
Since I can't stay hidden,

764
00:43:14,750 --> 00:43:16,330
I'll just scare you all to death.

765
00:43:17,400 --> 00:43:18,260
Scare you to death!

766
00:43:45,210 --> 00:43:46,700
What's going on here?

767
00:43:47,880 --> 00:43:49,680
Can't figure it out.

768
00:43:50,820 --> 00:43:52,140
Here, Sir,

769
00:43:52,170 --> 00:43:53,420
your skewers are ready.

770
00:43:53,760 --> 00:43:54,730
Here, Sir.

771
00:43:54,770 --> 00:43:55,550
-Take care.
-Thank you.

772
00:43:55,580 --> 00:43:57,450
-See you next time.
-Sir.

773
00:44:01,700 --> 00:44:02,760
What is that?

774
00:44:03,710 --> 00:44:05,030
I'll tell Jing about it.

775
00:44:06,700 --> 00:44:08,040
Jing, look!

776
00:44:08,080 --> 00:44:09,520
Isn't that our boss?

777
00:44:09,860 --> 00:44:11,080
It really is!

778
00:44:11,440 --> 00:44:12,730
Wait, cover for me.

779
00:44:12,750 --> 00:44:14,480
I need to talk to him about something.

780
00:44:15,180 --> 00:44:16,310
-Sure, no problem.
-Okay.

781
00:44:16,690 --> 00:44:17,620
I'll get back to making skewers.

782
00:44:17,670 --> 00:44:19,060
Go!

783
00:44:21,920 --> 00:44:23,270
What are you daydreaming about?

784
00:44:23,290 --> 00:44:25,280
My skewers are burnt!

785
00:44:32,370 --> 00:44:34,260
Is this opera?

786
00:44:35,410 --> 00:44:37,480
Why are they performing in the street?

787
00:44:41,500 --> 00:44:42,470
What are you looking at?

788
00:44:51,210 --> 00:44:52,470
Give me ten skewers, same as them.

789
00:44:52,500 --> 00:44:53,340
That many?

790
00:44:53,890 --> 00:44:55,650
It's over!

791
00:44:56,970 --> 00:45:00,980
I can't be the Top Belle anymore!

792
00:45:03,320 --> 00:45:05,520
What's this? I've never seen it before.

793
00:45:05,540 --> 00:45:07,310
This? It's called Lover's Tears.

794
00:45:07,450 --> 00:45:08,940
Isn't it written on the sign?

795
00:45:08,970 --> 00:45:11,690
"An endless resemblance to heartbreak poison,

796
00:45:11,720 --> 00:45:13,720
scattered as lover's tears."

797
00:45:14,280 --> 00:45:15,860
Sounds interesting.

798
00:45:15,880 --> 00:45:17,980
Young Master Wang, your poem's been plagiarized.

799
00:45:19,610 --> 00:45:21,080
So, that's

800
00:45:21,110 --> 00:45:23,210
the person who writes poems for us?

801
00:45:23,310 --> 00:45:25,160
Today, whatever he eats is on the house.

802
00:45:25,260 --> 00:45:26,860
Great!

803
00:45:26,910 --> 00:45:27,590
Young Master Wang,

804
00:45:28,540 --> 00:45:29,610
once you taste

805
00:45:29,700 --> 00:45:33,190
this flavor, you'll never forget it.

806
00:45:34,020 --> 00:45:35,290
Then give me ten skewers too.

807
00:45:35,330 --> 00:45:36,200
I want them for free too.

808
00:45:36,630 --> 00:45:38,670
Who are you to get ten skewers?

809
00:45:38,700 --> 00:45:40,030
He's the one who gets them for free.

810
00:45:40,050 --> 00:45:41,300
I'll help him eat them.

811
00:45:42,070 --> 00:45:43,660
You'll help him eat?

812
00:45:43,920 --> 00:45:46,740
You’re not thinking of helping him with pooping too, are you?

813
00:45:48,580 --> 00:45:50,060
Why are you so vulgar?

814
00:45:50,100 --> 00:45:51,690
You're selling food, yet you've ruined my appetite.

815
00:45:51,710 --> 00:45:52,440
Alright.

816
00:45:52,470 --> 00:45:54,930
You're all regular customers. Ten skewers each.

817
00:45:54,950 --> 00:45:56,580
It's fine, take them and eat.

818
00:45:56,720 --> 00:45:58,040
Take them and eat.

819
00:45:58,060 --> 00:45:59,070
Take them and eat.

820
00:45:59,590 --> 00:46:00,830
Take them and eat.

